item.title: How and Why I make my Etch A Sketch art permanent!
item.description: Hi Imgurians! It's been a minnit eh? Hope you're all doing well this holiday season! This isn't my first time addressing the subject of Etch A Sketch preservation in video form, but it's the first time I've made attempts to explain how the art erases otherwise, and why I do it! Hopefully this helps get ahead of a few understandable follow-up questions but if you have more I'm all for entertaining your additional queries! My one regret when making this video is not saying "perfunctory postal punt UPON your porch". Across probably makes more sense though. Fun art available at https://princessetch.com/ weeeee!
